fields.title: A 1 Dollar Recogniser Algorithm
fields.text:
We are living through the age of major advancements in AI, and a particularly interesting subfield of AI is Machine Learning. For many, including myself, and other people who study computer science related subjects at university level, this area is highly mystified and seems elusive without advanced knowledge of programming and statistics.

 

I have only just began scratching the surface of machine learning and can't give you a definite answer yet. But I know some basic stats, have programming experience and a genuine interest in the matter. I invite you on this journey with me to explore the depths of machine learning and how it can be applied to make our lives easier.
